          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "An enriched Zn-64 target, isotopic composition -",
                "Zn-64 is 99.4%, Zn-66 is 0.39%, Zn-67 is 0.04%,",
                "Zn-68 is 0.15% and Zn-30 is 0.02%, was used. The foils",
                "used were of thickness 320-mum or 325-mum.",
                "The natural target material (several Zn-nat targets",
                "were irradiated for optimization of the experimental",
                "set-up and radiochemistry procedures) was natural Zn",
                "99.98% and Ti-natural 99.6% for monitor foils.",
                "Foils, together with a 30-mum Ti-nat monitor were",
                "placed in a standard aluminium target holder and fixed",
                "with a 0.7-cm diameter aluminium collimator."
              ]
            }
          ],
